description: Rough wooden drying racks are arranged around the perimeters of the clearing, spread with animal hides in various states of tanning, and the stench that rises from the dilapidated hut near the racks hangs like a foul mist in the air.  Scraps of fur and half-dried flesh litter the ground amid tufts of scrawny weeds.
